## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="67c85-268">這個屬性由<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>期間<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>來決定是否使用參數值的原始或目前的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="67c85-268">This property is used by the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> during the <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to determine whether the original or current value is used for a parameter value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="67c85-269">這可讓更新的主索引鍵。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="67c85-269">This lets primary keys be updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="67c85-270">此屬性設定為新版<xref:System.Data.DataRow>供<xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性 (<xref:System.Data.DataRow>索引子)，或<xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法<xref:System.Data.DataRow>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="67c85-270">This property is set to the version of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> used by the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.Item%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property (<xref:System.Data.DataRow> indexer), or the <xref:System.Data.DataRow.GetChildRows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method of the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> object.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="67c85-271">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter>並設定其部分屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="67c85-271">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter("pDName", OracleType.VarChar)  
